org.jasig.cas.authentication

Interface AuthenticationContext

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultAuthenticationContext

    public interface AuthenticationContext
    The AuthenticationContext is an abstraction on top of a given authentication request. An authentication context carries the primary and composite authentication event, collected from all authentication attempts. The principal and attributes associated with this authentication are collected out of all events.
    Since:
    4.2
